{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Cozy Desktop Konbini</strong></u> is a cozy and relaxing idle game about managing a Konbini that stays at the bottom of your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/Desktop_With_Arrow.gif?t=1739435963\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Everything is Automated</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your Konbini runs smoothly on its own\u2014restock shelves, serve customers, and earn money, all while you focus on other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multitasking</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This idle game sits at the bottom of your screen, letting you manage your shop while studying, working, or just relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Decorate your Konbini</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your tiny Konbini with shelves, displays, and decorations to create the coziest shopping experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/Building_600.gif?t=1739435963\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock New Products and Buildings</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your Konbini with new shelves, vending machines, and unique products to attract more customers and grow your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Make a tiny gym</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some exercise wouldn\u2019t hurt, right? Add a small gym section to your Konbini and let your customers work out while they shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/Final_gym.gif?t=1739435963\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph